fields.name: The "pb" command
fields.value:
``` z/pb all/list

-> Gets all of Zodi's PBs through history.```

fields.name: ​
fields.value:
``` z/pb current <version>

-> Gets Zodi's current PB.```

fields.name: ​
fields.value:
``` z/pb new/add <version> <time>

-> Appends a new PB, where <version> is the game version you played on and <time> is the time to be added to the list.```

fields.name: ​
fields.value:
``` z/pb remove/removelast

-> Removes the last entry in the PBs list.```
